{"tid":434722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一對分咗手嘅情侶仲維持咁嘅關係 即係點","createTime":"2017-10-13T14:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T18:56:52.000Z","uid":153034,"like":709,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"72702cd4fff90f4ab866327d8b1d96ae9bb5ca0a","tid":434722,"uid":153034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"有個女仔朋友，前幾個月同longd男朋友分咗手 條仔有偷食前科+臨分手打到佢周身傷晒（佢兩個隻秋）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前排同佢出街 見個男仔仲有whatsapp搵佢 覆慢少少就炸佢chat room 問佢咩事 佢話係個男仔死纏爛打 想追返佢 佢都唔係好想理個ex 依加都收咗幾個兵 收咗啲禮物咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就走去問佢個ex做咩要死纏爛打 點知佢個ex同我講話「佢晚晚都有同我講bb good night,miss you果啲。我過兩個星期就會返香港 佢話肯同我去旅行(個男仔請) 你理得我地」我個fd好似即場俾人揭穿咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話個男仔咁講 佢咪咁講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地果個時候唔係情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一對分咗手嘅情侶仲維持咁樣 即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正評：臭雞<br />\n負評：真愛"},{"pid":"2b768c8c77daa7c37ea83d0fb3813645fa602692","tid":434722,"uid":81214,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"一次不忠&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"eaff6a076cc6a03e53ef3b213ed6a7151f47ab8d","tid":434722,"uid":2419,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"即係你冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68aed340e4001da4bd93501a5ca78402cf903fd","tid":434722,"uid":153034,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係你冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/face